The Insects: An Outline of Entomology (5th Edition)


2014 | ISBN-10: 111884615X | 624 pages | PDF | 25 MB

Insects represent over half of the planets biological diversity. 

This popular textbook provides a comprehensive introduction to this extraordinary diversity, and places entomology central to the theory and practice of evolutionary and ecological studies.
